name: CZ-4
Lore: 'Very common communications droid. Some have been modified to be defense drones. Programmed to warn their masters of an imminent attack.',
Text: 'Opponent may not ''react'' to or from same site. You may ''react'' to a battle or Force drain at same or adjacent Jabba''s Palace site by deploying (at normal use of the Force) one non-unique alien to that site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
